Al Ain, Abu Dhabi
Our client is a 500 + bed tertiary hospital which seeks to recruit a female Obstetrician and Gynaecologist who holds a HAAD Specialist License.
Key Performance Goals:
Provide a safe and effective medical service compatible with JCI standards Ensure effective clinical governance, audit and risk management systems are followed Educate and supervise Residents and Medical Students
Qualifications and Experience
Medical Degree Residency in O&G; Postgraduate qualification in O&G; listed in Tier 1, 2 or 3 of HAAD PQR. HAAD Specialist License
The position attracts a generous salary and benefits package which is tax free at source.
